{
  "stem": "25835.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very, very upsetting us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nobody supposed it could be.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "17 Of September-- they, they came without warning, sending people to Siberia or killing people without any reason because they are Polish [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This mean ?] not simple people, but some special.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know why it was so bad attitude.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But since centuries, we know that we are between two giants.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "1939, the same-- 17 days after German army attacked Poland, only 17 days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly when he reopened something, when he start to work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because he was energetic person and hard-working.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How they survived these first days, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Only I remember that my school start to be in-- this building was evacuated because command-- German commander took it, nice building.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we start to have classes in different small houses-- to-- our teachers continue this teaching work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it was forbidden to have geography and history, only German language.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was, of course, necessary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you see, slowly, but we have underground education concerning history and geography.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember my teacher-- oh, it was nice person.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I finish seven, seven grade in-- during occupation.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But was very difficult because always was German looking for people to arrest and take to, to working camp or to concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Life in this time-- I was in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In this time was very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Even if you took tram, overcrowded.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But you never know if a soldier will stop them, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they took for killing, or to concentration, or to working camp-- very unsafe life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Food was also very, very poor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Usually, we had [INAUDIBLE] small and was couple, couple marmalade from beets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "No-- everybo-- everything what we can eat, it was necessary to buy on private places.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
